author: Cleo Abram
description:
Did you know that there’s a tiny little galaxy orbiting OUR galaxy… and it goes through us all the time!

This is our galaxy - the Milky Way, and THAT is the Sagittarius DWARF Galaxy. 

And when the two collide, this is what happens… 

For more optimistic science and technology, subscribe!

title: This Tiny Galaxy Is Orbiting Us
